<h1>Developer</h1>

<p>This section is for developers building on top of grigson — implementing a custom renderer, integrating the parser into a tool, or working with the programmatic APIs.</p>
<p>If you want to write chord charts and render them in a web page, start with the <a href="{{ '/language/' | url }}">Language</a> reference and <a href="{{ '/renderers/' | url }}">Renderers</a> instead.</p>

